{"word":"G2755 - κενόδοξος - kenódoxos - ken-od'-ox-os - Desirous of vain-glory","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κενόδοξος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kenódoxos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ken-od'-ox-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Desirous of vain-glory"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வீண்புகழ்ச்சியை விரும்புதல் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"glorying without reason, conceited, vain - glorious, eager for empty glory"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2756 - κενός - kenós - ken-os'/2756\">G2756</a> and <a href=\"#/G1391 - δόξα - dóxa - dox'-ah/1391\">G1391</a>; <i>vainly glorifying</i>, that is, <i>self conceited:</i> - desirous of vain-glory."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2754 - κενοδοξία - kenodoxía - ken-od-ox-ee'-ah/2754\">G2754</a>, <a href=\"#/G2755 - κενόδοξος - kenódoxos - ken-od'-ox-os/2755\">G2755</a>, <a href=\"#/G2756 - κενός - kenós - ken-os'/2756\">G2756</a>, <a href=\"#/G2757 - κενοφωνία - kenophōnía - ken-of-o-nee'-ah/2757\">G2757</a>, <a href=\"#/G2758 - κενόω - kenóō - ken-o'-o/2758\">G2758</a>, <a href=\"#/G2761 - κενῶς - kenōs - ken-oce'/2761\">G2761</a>"}]}